                <dt>Physical Descriptions</dt>
        <dd>
          <dl>
                          <dt>Medium</dt>
              <dd>Brown ink and gray wash over graphite and black chalk on cream antique laid paper, framing line in black ink and gold wash; verso: graphite tracing of two figures from upper left recto</dd>
            
           
           
                          <dt>Dimensions</dt>
              <dd>18.6 x 18.7 cm (7 5/16 x 7 3/8 in.)</dd>
            
            
            
            
            
                          <dt>Inscriptions and Marks</dt>
              <dd>
                                  <ul class="unstyled-list">
                    
