                        </li>
                                              <li data-a="2">
                          watermark: Arms of Bern; related to Lindt 131 (House of Gruner, Zeender, and Koch, “Zu Thal” mill, Bern, 1640– 43)
                        </li>
                                              <li data-a="2">
